d sat on her kitchen couch and hummed as she cooked. I had had the experience of becoming one with the melody, a melody psalm-like and desolate—I tried to make it come back to me. <em>I fly through the darkness to be with you</em>, I sang over and over as the train moved through the dark fields, constantly changing the melody so that it would not sound like a pop song, but beautiful, dignified, like an open gray valley.</p><p>What was she going through her head right now? What did she need to get through this moment of her life?</p><p>Dad had texted and said she wanted to know when I was coming, and I had the feeling that she was holding out for me: I would run for her. As we rolled into Uppsala. I started to stretch. Behind me, the ladies commented that the man at the door was getting ready for his run, laughing. I began running in place to warm up.</p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5fe264c5-2c39-4bca-8c12-20a17296a198_256x256.png" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/wIKkIHTbkc9VKajRlU_sse41pGh06gvqB0Q_hTsPb6Q=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX3dlYnAscV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkY1ZmUyNjRjNS0yYzM5LTRiY2EtOGMxMi0yMGExNzI5NmExOThfMjU2eDI1Ni5wbmc= 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/eQsZIkNln2aDeyYyAR4WJ3qvVFfJ-aKAH7aMB6xSus0=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd184NDgsY19saW1pdCxmX3dlYnAscV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkY1ZmUyNjRjNS0yYzM5LTRiY2EtOGMxMi0yMGExNzI5NmExOThfMjU2eDI1Ni5wbmc= 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/t7LSFkw1Wjer0029u8eK15CDaN2StpfdLA_nGK-x